item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - VERY RARE ALBUM - Athena Cage - The Art Of a Woman (2001)
item.description:
Hi Guys,

I cant afford to spend £100 on this VERY RARE R&B album by Athena Age called The Art Of A Woman.
(She was the lead singer of Kut Klose.)

The album was never released, but it must be online somewhere in HQ or can someone get it in FLAC or 320kps?
(Only about 100 copies were made.)

https://www.discogs.com/release/14551472-Athena-Cage-The-Art-Of-A-Woman

https://www.allmusic.com/album/the-art-of-a-woman-mw0000589760

https://tower.jp/item/680801/The-Art-Of-A-Woman


Can anyone make my entire life and get this? I know theres some amazing people on here with access to a lot online.


HUGE THANKS x
